        "description": "Arcadia isn't another sports sim – it's the beginning of an entirely new Mixed Reality sport.\n\nHere, your hands have superpowers that allow you to manipulate the Arcadia-01 ball in ways that defy the limits of reality. Send it soaring with the push of your palm, then pull it back a split second later.\n\nSmash targets through a portal a continent away. Move with the Arcadia-01 ball. Feel it in your fingertips, feel it in your whole body. This is the AR-01, the first ball of a new era in sports.\n\nWe've taken what we love most about traditional sports and combined it with ideas that could only exist in mixed reality to create a new sport category that truly belongs to the new generation of athletes. This isn't about pressing buttons; it's about moving your body, honing your reflexes, and mastering a skill ceiling that stretches as high as you're willing to put the work in.\n\nThe Arcadia app is your training ground – forge your skills and compete at home, then bring them to the full-scale Arcadia court to become an Arcadia Champion.\n\nWelcome to Arcadia. Play Every Dimension.",
